  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-11-05T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18546b946500",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-11-05T09:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "2",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185446501",
    "parent_block_id": "page-root",
    "text": "School-year take-home runs about $1,800 a month against itemized expenses of $1,603, leaving a real buffer near $197. This is the number to plan against now, not the Whitfield summer months.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-11-05T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18546b946501",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-11-05T09:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "3",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185446501",
    "parent_block_id": "page-root",
    "text": "Whitfield summer take-home was about $2,300 against the same expenses, a buffer near $697. That comfort ended when the stipend months ended.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-11-05T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18546b946502",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-11-05T09:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "4",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185446501",
    "parent_block_id": "page-root",
    "text": "Any month with more than one application fee will run tight against the $197 buffer.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  }
]
